{"tid":2299202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"裁判官鄭念慈：盲目相信朋友 係不合常理","createTime":"2020-11-24T14:54:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T16:30:30.000Z","uid":321059,"like":10,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"29071487ee815287234668b6f6171b56d8d41bfc","tid":2299202,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:54:02.000Z","msg":"去年9月13日中秋節，網上傳出紅磡海韻軒海景酒店有警員舉辦婚禮，有市民晚上於附近聚集，警方到場驅散並截查多人。一名海關關員被搜獲對講機，被控一項無牌管有無線電通訊器具罪，經審訊後，今（24日）在九龍城裁判法院被裁定罪成，罰款5,000元。<br />\n<br />\n被告的中學同學伍展邦出庭作供，稱現正經營藥房，因工作需要而在店內使用無線對講機，案發當日攜帶兩部對講機到深水埗修理，但因為電單車儲物空間不足，所以將其中一部對講機放在電單車儲物格，另一部則放在腰包，並將腰包交給被告保管，因此林攜有的對講機不屬於林。伍亦是本案原本的另一被告，同樣被控無牌管有無線電通訊器具罪，早前獲准自簽守行為方式處理控罪。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官鄭念慈裁決時指，林熾輝2014年入職海關，工作期間必會遇到自稱代別人攜帶物品的人，基於林的職業、知識、學歷及經驗，他必會特別小心，<span class=\"red\">故不相信林被朋友要求代為保管背包時，會盲目相信對方；林對於朋友交託的背包不加以察看，做法不合常理。鄭官指，唯一不可抗拒的推論是，林清楚知道背包內藏有無線對講機，故裁定他罪成。</span>林的親友及伍展邦聽聞裁決後，在庭上紛紛落淚。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1079075\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1079075&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=191fd253\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1079075&h=fe7540d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1079075</a><br />\n<br />\n做得朋友 好多時都係講個信字<br />\n鄭官其實係咪一個朋友都無<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1df18e79691200fc5579099aa73b548bd950a9d","tid":2299202,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:55:57.000Z","msg":"為便衣警急救<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8621443220457cd2723c635c48bdef4d153a02bb","tid":2299202,"uid":24814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:57:18.000Z","msg":"吓 屌你老味 未有呢單嘢之前邊個知對講機唔帶得"},{"pid":"3a4d35b61518283b895e6f67b2b5fd75e0f2f554","tid":2299202,"uid":321059,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:57:39.000Z","msg":"黑警私下用對講機就訓斥了事<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201124/RRSRJHIGV5DZFOMPD337BGOWME/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201124%2FRRSRJHIGV5DZFOMPD337BGOWME%2F&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=9c86f483\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201124%2FRRSRJHIGV5DZFOMPD337BGOWME%2F&h=618555f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201124/RRSRJHIGV5DZFOMPD337BGOWME/</a>"},{"pid":"978c215f02db959972c7192d36de468afe098b46","tid":2299202,"uid":34869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:59:07.000Z","msg":"其實罪唔罪成佢都冇可能做番果份工<br />\n根本當佢黃絲黎打<br />\n比人起曬底仲點做"},{"pid":"95628b4e8b037fb4a182c01b12e4fc3a180448f9","tid":2299202,"uid":43062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:59:12.000Z","msg":"上訴啦咁撚主觀判都得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57875f2fc7490c53f4938caf62063417f610fa3b","tid":2299202,"uid":245849,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:59:28.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢係冇朋友定係冇常識<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1505dc41fef47fcc5fa43b677f1bf9356372b8ce","tid":